# Company/Product Background Information

This file contains information about your company and products that will be used by the AI
to generate personalized outreach messages. The AI will use this context to make relevant
connections between news events and your solutions.

## Instructions

1. Copy this file to `background_info.txt`
2. Add as much detail as you want about:
   - Your company/product overview
   - Key features and capabilities
   - Target industries and use cases
   - Recent achievements, benchmarks, or case studies
   - Unique selling points
   - Technical specifications (if relevant)

3. The AI will read this entire file, so you can add:
   - Multiple paragraphs
   - Bullet points
   - Technical details
   - Case studies
   - Performance metrics
   - Whatever information helps create better outreach messages

## Example Format

### Company Overview
[Your company description here]

### Products and Services
- Product 1: [Description]
- Product 2: [Description]

### Key Features
- Feature 1
- Feature 2

### Use Cases
- Industry 1: [How you help]
- Industry 2: [How you help]

### Recent Achievements
- [Benchmark results]
- [Customer success stories]
- [Awards or recognition]

### Unique Selling Points
- [What makes you different]
- [Key competitive advantages]

---

The more specific and detailed you are, the better the AI can tailor outreach messages
to each company's news and situation.
